                "url": "/topics/once"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/townsend_harris_237666",
        "quote": "It will be quite satisfactory if you open them gradually, as the circumstances may require; but the President assures you that this will not be the case if you make a treaty with England first.",
